  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve] [Aegiomon]: Cost 3 \n\n\uFF1CSecurity A. +1\uFF1E
    \n\uFF1CDecode ([Aegiomon])\uFF1E (When this Digimon would leave the battle area
